import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Card, CardImg, CardBody,
    CardTitle, CardSubtitle, Form, FormGroup, Badge, Input, Media} from 'reactstrap';
export default class MainCard extends Component {
  
  render() {
    return (
        <Card>
 <CardBody>
        <CardSubtitle>   
        <Media>
      <Media left href=
      "data:image/png;base64,">
        <Media object data-src="holder.js/64x64" alt="" />
      </Media>
      <Media body>
        <Media heading>
          Media heading
        </Media>
       1 hours ago
         </Media>

         <Badge color="primary" pill>+ Follow</Badge>
    </Media>
        </CardSubtitle>
        </CardBody>
        <CardBody>
          <CardTitle> <CardImg src="data:image/jpeg;base64," 
          /> </CardTitle>       
         

        </CardBody>
        <CardBody>
        <CardSubtitle>Custom</CardSubtitle>
        </CardBody>
        <CardBody>
        <CardSubtitle>Chopper</CardSubtitle>
        </CardBody>
        <CardBody>
        <CardSubtitle>
            <Form>
        <FormGroup>
          <Input type="text" name="comment" id="comment" placeholder="Add Comment ..." />
        </FormGroup>
        </Form>
        </CardSubtitle>
        </CardBody>
        <CardBody>
        <CardSubtitle>View Comment</CardSubtitle>
        </CardBody>
        
      </Card>
    )
  }
}
